"tid":2352964,"uid":208021,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T19:00:40.000Z","msg":"建議唔好貪平買呢部<br />\n呢部撞溫度牆撞得好犀利 90幾度話咁易<br />\n打機不停thermal throttling真係會好撚頹<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利伸：中過伏"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T19:06:15.000Z","msg":"有冇邊部推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T01:48:02.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過砌部desktop<br />\n如非必要 要gaming體驗好一律建議desktop<br />\n<br />\n買gaming laptop都係睇筆直做人<br />\n再者你要keep得部機好<br />\n一個好嘅散熱底座係必不可少<br />\n當然都要取決於部機本身散熱設計如何<br />\n否則加塊幾靚嘅散熱底座都只係哂氣<br />\n<br />\n因為長期過熱只會不斷消耗硬件嘅壽命<br />\nperformance會打折<br />\nThermal throttling就會越黎越頻密<br />\n<br />\n如有必要非gaming laptop不可<br />\n揀機戈陣唔好揀薄機 儘量買厚身啲嘅<br />\n<br />\n我就唔推薦邊部啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為我都只係用過兩部laptop<br />\n(第一部就係predator<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第二部係msi)<br />\n最後都轉戰desktop<br />\n<br />\n建議樓主做足功課 根據自己需要<br />\nE.g.咩lv嘅效能 價錢 外觀 <br />\n上網搵相關型號嘅評測<br />\n留意performance, temperature, battery, noise level etc.<br />\n保養都好緊要<br />\n如果要再平啲 可考慮amazon買 但保養就麻煩<br />\n<br />\n下面個po都有好多有心巴打解答notebook問題<br />\n祝樓主可以搵到部心儀又滿意嘅型號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nNotebook討論區 及 外國網購Notebook推介 (52)，新手請睇下#1-2<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2323957\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2323957</a>"},{"pid":"85e8c9a82b8536b6a4bc470b473220c65e75397c","tid":2352964,"uid":171128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4576d4646141712005d1b946ca9470f4d278c68b","tid":2352964,"uid":208021,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T19:00:40.000Z","msg":"建議唔好貪平買呢部<br />\n呢部撞溫度牆撞得好犀利 90幾度話咁易<br />\n打機不停thermal throttling真係會好撚頹<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利伸：中過伏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T04:37:59.000Z"